@NODE History
@TITLE "snes9xstarter À History"


    @{b}History@{ub}


    2.0 (03.03.2004)  - first public release

    2.1 (25.04.2004)  - fixed a memory leak bug (main class was
                        not freed)

    2.2 (18.05.2004)  - fixed another memory leak (diskobject was
                        not freed)
                      - makes now use of get9.library
    
    2.3 (05.11.2004)  - second public release

@ENDNODE

